(define/contract (good-subsetof-binary-matrix grid)
  (-> (listof (listof exact-integer?)) (listof exact-integer?))

  (define (is-good-subset rows)
    (let ((k (length rows)))
      (let loop ((j 0) (valid #t))
        (if (or (not valid) (>= j (length (car grid))))
            valid
            (let ((sum (foldl (lambda (row acc) (+ acc (list-ref row j))) 0 rows)))
              (loop (+ j 1) (and valid (<= sum (floor (/ k 2))))))))))

  (define (subsets lst)
    (if (null? lst)
        '(())
        (let ((ss (subsets (cdr lst))))
          (append ss (map (lambda (s) (cons (car lst) s)) ss)))))

  (define (find-good-subset)
    (let* ((indices (range (length grid)))
           (all-subsets (subsets indices))
           (good-subsets (filter (lambda (s) (and (not (null? s)) (is-good-subset (map (lambda (i) (list-ref grid i)) s)))) all-subsets)))
      (if (null? good-subsets) '() (car good-subsets))))

  (find-good-subset))
